Tracy Vilar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracy_Vilar 0 Tracy Vilar (born Tracy Leigh Vilar April 12, 1968; and sometimes credited Tracy Villars) is an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Ro-Ro on the CBS sitcom Partners, Sophia Ortiz on The WB sitcom The Steve Harvey Show, and Angela de la Cruz on the TNT television show, Saved.
